00:00:06.580 --> 00:00:09.280 align:middle line:10%
>> The fields of neuroscience
and technology are emerging

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:10.750 align:middle line:10%
in amazing ways.

00:00:10.750 --> 00:00:14.320 align:middle line:10%
